{"tid":1613262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日諗咗個新口號","createTime":"2019-10-02T13:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:35:39.000Z","uid":159155,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f234c58620b26b57cd456c7eafaf8055abbe8b","tid":1613262,"uid":159155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">驅逐共黨獨立香港</span></span><br />\n呢幾個月嘅事蹟睇到共產黨對香港嘅干涉，<br />\n呢排又講赤納粹，將目標對準共產黨能夠獲得國際關注及支持，之前有唔少po都指出獨立先係我哋唯一出路。呢個口號既表達出香港人要 驅逐共產黨出香港，同時點明咗香港需要獨立， 擺脫共產黨控制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係同陳雲個口號好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望遲啲聽到大家嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc697c90f0bc230f9793758748c0aaea560b67ab","tid":1613262,"uid":159155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:29:57.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"f4dd77600fabad9534f49df4c5a9c5f82b616b51","tid":1613262,"uid":159155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7f064c7fc289749ab8539679cb1063bdb41edc5e","tid":1613262,"uid":159155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:30:18.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"daf4261f82111b3aaa369e93010468f3e4609d96","tid":1613262,"uid":159155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"03c0989cf9b4156aad6716a30bd29894e132419f","tid":1613262,"uid":159155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:30:38.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"28af197899ecaaaa559420d2e3e4dc43fb5c19e7","tid":1613262,"uid":159155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:30:48.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"fe1f7e9988837d3bf90b69c769451f4cbf3e122e","tid